	module for the Apache server.  If you are already running a
	recent version of the <a href="http://stronghold.c2.net/">
	<b>Stronghold Secure Webserver</b></a>, then the necessary
	code has already been included with your server -- you simply
	need to turn it on.  For earlier versions of Apache, you can
	use <a href="apache-fastcgi.tgz"> this <b>mod_fastcgi.c</b></a>.
	
